      "description": "  ## BuddyBridge 1.0.8\r\n\r\n  ### 新增\r\n  - 设置页增加 WorkBuddy 路径填写提示（含自定义安装指引）\r\n  - README 增加手动查找 CodeBuddy 路径说明\r\n  - README 增加权限授权提示词章节\r\n  - 新增 workbuddy/ 目录，含初始化提示词文件\r\n\r\n  ### 修复\r\n  - API 版本兼容性优化\r\n\r\n  ### What's New\r\n  - Added WorkBuddy path hint in settings with custom install guide\r\n  - Added manual CodeBuddy path finding instructions in README\r\n  - Added permission authorization section in README\r\n  - Added workbuddy/ setup prompts for new environment initialization\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n\r\n  **注意**：本插件为非官方第三方集成，需要配合 WorkBuddy / CodeBuddy 本地服务使用。\r\n  **Note**: This is an unofficial third-party plugin. Requires WorkBuddy / CodeBuddy local service.",
